The Quesadilla was awesome.
They put Green Chiles in the Quesadilla if you ask for it and believe me, you want them....they are sooo good!
It's what makes this Quesadilla unique and tasty.
Overall, it was a pretty good meal.
Not sure I would drive all the way across town to have it again, but if I am in the area I would consider making a short drive.
