I love both but I can't live without my Hatch chili!
Everything I have had here is super tasty!
Love when they bring the BBQ pit out front and you can get racks of ribs to go at a super reasonable price.
Although everything has been great there, they have the best breakfast burritos I have ever had!
Sorry mom.
I always get the chorizo, smothered christmas tree style!
(red and green chili for the novice)  For those who don't like the spicier side of life, they have other great options to satisfy your hunger pangs.
Just don't forget your sopapillas!
They will make your tastebuds so happy, you might forget the spice that just reaked havoc on your tongue!
My opinion--GO!
